Text: Re EnronOnline Credit Derivatives Propsoed Reference EntitiesI apologise for the delay The developers were travelling and I had to literally chase them to get a response It appears that we do not have business relationships with the entities listed by you No MOU or Non Disclosure Agreements have been signed although there are discussions going on with a couple of entities Sandeep Katwala AM To Lena KasbekarENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT cc Subject EnronOnline Credit Derivatives Propsoed Reference Entities Forwarded by Sandeep KatwalaENRONDEVELOPMENT on AM Rob Walls PM To Legal Mgmt cc Mark CT Subject EnronOnline Credit Derivatives Propsoed Reference Entities Please review the attached and let me know asap if any of these entities have relationships with your business units Thanks Forwarded by Rob WallsENRONDEVELOPMENT on PM From Mark CT on PM To Michael NRON Kristina MordauntEnron nron Communications Vicki ES Rob WallsENRON NRONDEVELOPMENT cc Mark E CT Subject EnronOnline Credit Derivatives Propsoed Reference Entities As we discussed attached is the new list of proposed reference entities I have also attached my previous memo outlining the propsosed business and our concerns
